channel.title: Wrote 2 programs in Visual Basic, tell me what you think
channel.description:
Videos demonstrating the programs are avalaible at: http://www.armeniasurf.tk http://www.vregenator-website-hacker.tk
I worked on these 2 projects lately. Both are written in Visual Basic (wich is a language based on C++ only it's more user-friedly). Tell me what you think:
[b]Armenia Surf:[/b]
Armenia Surf, the first Armenian webbrowser! Armenia Surf is an advanced webbrowser with alot of cool features. It is coded by Vreg from Vreg Productions in Visual Basic. No installing needed. It imports all the plugins and all your saved accounts from Internet Explorer. It is an extremely fast webbrowser because there are no useless applications running in background like in Internet Explorer, Mozilla Firefox, ... This webbrowser runs it's own process, it doesn't open another iexplore.exe so that makes it even more faster. Download it at: http://www.armeniasurf.tk

[IMG]http://i290.photobucket.com/albums/ll242/VregScapeOwner/Untitled3-2.png[/img]
[b]Vregenator Website Hacker:[/b]
Alright, I made a tool for all the noobies out there who dream to hack but don't know how to. With this noob friendly tool you can easly hack websites. It has a built-in checker to see if your selected website is vulnerble and a built-in vulnerble website searcher. Hacking websites was never so easy. !!!READ THE INSTRUCTIONS WHEN USING THE PROGRAM!!! In this video I'm showing how powerful this tool is by hacking some websites. Download it at: http://www.vregenator-website-hacker.tk
Q: How does this work?
A: It hacks a website by performing an automated SQL Injection, I pre-programmed 16 scripts to the program, the first script (Injection 1) is the best one.
